messages.messageBody:
Kandy, that's unbelievable! I've always wondered about these
folk who get pregnant while they're on the pill or something and
don't notice cos they never had periods anyway. Thought there
must be some kind of mental block or some such. Your body
knows it's pregnant after all! But anyway, how are they doing?
Now that's some kind of home-birth!!! LOL And the Pastor? Is
he out of shock yet? Ya know, that's really the way to do it, isn't
it? no fuss, no worry, no stress. Just go to the toilet and get a
baby instead! now that's what I need, instead of what I've got
atm :-(

Stop rambling, woman! I AM fertile, i WILL get pregnant!!!!
Tracy

messages.subject: Didn't know she was pregnant!
messages.msgSnippet: Goodness sakes, I have a friend in another state who just had a baby one day last week.  She didn t know she was pregnant!!!  How on earth do you ~DO~ that???
messages.messageBody:
Goodness sakes, I have a friend in another state who just had a
baby one day last week. She didn't know she was pregnant!!! How
on earth do you ~DO~ that???

She says she didn't feel good and that she felt like she needed to
use the bathroom and couldn't. When her dad got home from running
errands (she is 21 and living with her father who is a Pastor),
she handed him the new 5 lb 12 oz baby girl.

All he could think to say was "sit down until your mother gets
home" LOL!

Blessings to you,

Kandy
